    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚证券投资委员会副主席表示将在澳大利亚证券交易所民事诉讼中寻求未来处罚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asic-deputy-chair-says-seeks-future-penalties-in-asx-civil-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚市场监管机构起诉澳大利亚证券交易所有限公司 (ASX Ltd.)，指控其在多年来对一项技术项目的进展和延迟的担忧中发表误导性言论，随后该监管机构计划寻求处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asic-deputy-chair-says-seeks-future-penalties-in-asx-civil-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SM投资：业务增长潜力巨大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/sm-investments-potential-for-business-growth-enormous-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SM Investments 财务执行副总裁 Franklin Gomez 表示，该公司业务的增长潜力巨大。他在“彭博市场：亚洲”节目中与 Paul Allen 和 Avril Hong 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/sm-investments-potential-for-business-growth-enormous-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚证券投资委员会 (ASIC) 起诉澳大利亚证券交易所 (ASX) 误导性陈述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/asic-sues-asx-over-misleading-statements-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚证券和投资委员会副主席 Sarah Court 讨论了该证券监管机构为何起诉 ASX，指控其在长达数年的清算和结算系统升级中发表误导性声明。她在“彭博市场亚洲”节目中与 Paul Allen 和 Avril Hong 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/asic-sues-asx-over-misleading-statements-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:54:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国罕见贷款下降引发“资产负债表”衰退担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国近二十年来首次缩减银行贷款，引发人们担忧中国这一全球第二大经济体正像日本几十年前那样陷入“资产负债表衰退”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国泰航空因利润问题成为全球被做空最多的航空公司股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/cathay-pacific-world-s-most-shorted-airline-stock-on-profit-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国泰航空有限公司目前是全球被做空最多的大型航空公司股票，尽管全球旅游业出现反弹，但航空业仍在努力提高利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/cathay-pacific-world-s-most-shorted-airline-stock-on-profit-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国交易商为避免监管审查而支付债券溢价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-traders-pay-premium-for-bonds-to-avoid-regulatory-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，中国交易员正在以溢价购买国债，以逃避监管机构对前所未有的股市上涨的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-traders-pay-premium-for-bonds-to-avoid-regulatory-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:30:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球最大钢铁生产商警告行业危机“严重”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-steel-industry-in-crisis-as-baowu-warns-of-severe-winter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家全球最大钢铁生产商警告称，中国钢铁行业正面临比 2008 年和 2015 年更为严重的危机，凸显出保留现金的必要性，并将当前形势比作“严冬”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-steel-industry-in-crisis-as-baowu-warns-of-severe-winter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市在美国 CPI 公布前上涨，新西兰元暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场预期即将发布的美国消费者物价报告将允许美联储在 9 月份开始放松货币政策，亚洲股市因此上涨。新西兰央行意外降息后，新西兰元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 22:30:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布勒旺霍华德 (Brevan Howard) 为亚洲信贷招聘新员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/brevan-howard-hires-david-nash-from-millennium-spinoff-modular</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月前，布勒万霍华德资产管理公司 (Brevan Howard Asset Management) 裁减了全球约 10% 的员工，如今该公司又聘请了安德鲁萨克斯顿 (Andrew Saxton) 和戴维纳什 (David Nash) 加入其亚洲信贷团队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/brevan-howard-hires-david-nash-from-millennium-spinoff-modular</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:25:10 GMT</pubDate>
